705209f-b.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - 3rd Street
705209f-b.text:
356-370 King's Highway, south side, between West 3rd and 4th Streets,] showing in the foreground, No. 370, the home of J.JJ. Kelly in 1871.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
The same, showimg the middle house (No. 366) renovated, and a full view of the last house. The Kelly house was demolished prior to 1929.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
